primary_outcome.description:
The percentage will be calculated separately as follows:
Number of positive GBS culture from vaginal/rectal swabs in all participants;
Number of positive GBS QF-PCR from vaginal/rectal swabs in all participants;
Number of positive GBS culture/QF-PCR from intrauterine swabs in women whose vaginal-rectal GBS test is positive;
Number of positive GBS culture from pharynx/rectal swabs in newborns whose mother 's vaginal-rectal GBS test is positive;
Number of positive GBS QF-PCR from pharynx/rectal swabs in newborns whose mother 's vaginal-rectal GBS test is positive;
